imy [Dockerfiles repository](https://github.com/xddxdd/dockerfiles),		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
ispecifically 14 (images) multiplied by 8 (architectures) to 112 jobs.		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
