iAn actual example can be found		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i[at this commit in my Dockerfiles repo](https://github.com/xddxdd/dockerfiles/blob/4268d0f076ee76efdff670e2f9b0dae5961a968f/.drone.jsonnet).		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
